@startuml state
title Operation states

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

[*] --> PENDING : analyzer\ndecides table is due

PENDING --> SCHEDULING : scheduler\nclaims for a bin
SCHEDULING --> SCHEDULED : job submitted\nto Jobs service

SCHEDULED --> [*] : history row written\n(SUCCESS or FAILED)

PENDING --> CANCELED : superseded\nby another PENDING

CANCELED --> [*]

@enduml
